These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, backgammon, billiard
House: gothic-revival, victorian, futuristic, modern
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, rock, techno
 1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 2. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 3. the fan rock is not to the right of the fan d&b##8
 4. the fan d&b is not to the left of the modern house##8
 5. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the fan rock##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is the fan country##1
 8. the fan rock is not the modern house##6
 9. the fan d&b is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
10. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the futuristic house##8
11. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
12. the fan d&b is between the person playing backgammon and the victorian house##2
13. the fan rock and the futuristic house have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | backgammon | scrabble      | billiard | chess |
| Job           | futuristic | modern | victorian      | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | d&b            | techno    | country |

