.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, filmmaking, magic-tricks, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, pakistani, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rugby, swimming, tennis
 1. the pakistani is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 3. the person who's sport is rugby and the colombian have the same parity positions##9
 4. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 7. the dutch is not to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the spanish##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the dutch##1
11. the colombian is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
12. the dutch is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
13. the dutch is on the left of the pakistani##1
14. the pakistani is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
