.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, lettuce, pear, cranberry
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, juice, tea
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, mouse, turtle
 1. the person eating onion is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 3. the person drinking juice is the person eating onion##1
 4. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 5. the person eating cranberry and the person drinking iced-tea have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person eating onion##8
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the owner of the bird is between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the turtle##2
11. the person eating lettuce is not the person drinking iced-tea##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | cranberry | pear     | onion  | lettuce |
| Nationality   | hot-chocolate       | iced-tea    | juice | tea |
| Pet           | mouse       | guinea-pig | bird     | turtle  |

