There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, black, apricot, mauve
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, rowing, sailing
 1. the person who growsbegonia and the person who likes apricot have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who likes black have different parity positions##9
 3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 4. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 7. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person who likes coral is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
10. the person who likes coral is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who likes apricot##2
11. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | rose  | marigold        | begonia  | poppy |
| Hobby      | black  | coral    | apricot | mauve |
| Sport      | rowing | ice-hockey | sailing | lacrosse    |

