 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the person who growspoppy is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 4. the fan ambient is on the right of the fan disco##1
 5. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
 6. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the fan house##5
 7. the fan house and the person who growspoppy have different parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the fan disco is not to the right of the fan ambient##8
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who growspoppy##6

